data.description: This stunning two-story home is located in a cul de sac and is one of the very few 5 bedroom 3 1/2 bath homes in the neighborhood. This home has all the room one needs for a large crew. The downstairs consists of a Master bedroom, living room, kitchen, breakfast area 1/2 bath plus flex room that can be used as a formal dining, office or another bedroom. The carpet downstairs has been replaced with tile floors. Main front door was replaced with a heavy metal custom glass door.  The upstairs has a large gameroom/family room, 2 full bathrooms and 4 bedrooms. Carpet in game room and 2 bedrooms and both bathrooms was replaced with water resistant wood floors.  The patio is just off the kitchen/breakfast room. True Texas size home. Low taxes Chambers County
